==Loot==
At current [[Grand Exchange]] prices, opening an essence impling jar gives {{Coins|{{ImpValue|essence|jar=yes}} round 0}} worth of loot, on average. This means opening essence impling jars marks an average profit of {{Coins|{{ImpValue|essence|jar=yes}}-{{GEP|Essence impling jar}} round 0}} per jar, however this does not include loot from clue scrolls.

On average, one would profit {{Coins|50*({{ImpValue|essence|jar=yes}}-{{GEP|Essence impling jar}}) round 0}} to get a [[clue scroll (medium)|medium clue scroll]] from essence impling jars at current [[Grand Exchange]] prices, excluding the rewards from the completed [[Treasure Trail]]s.

